    A simple implementation of ImmutableSet.

    The real set is given in the constructor, and only read operations are exposed. Note that one that holds a reference original set, can change it.
    This implementation only insures that one who gets a reference to the ImmutableSet cannot change it unless it also gets a reference to the original set.
